{"tid":2184040,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"To myself","createTime":"2020-09-01T09:52:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T15:31:12.000Z","uid":326957,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"eaa2ac8e81d9bb3eeac950ebc2a0857e50ff4550","tid":2184040,"uid":326957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:52:48.000Z","msg":"在夢中 <br />\n你告訴我：「不要不開心了，我想你開心起來」<br />\n<br />\n看到很久沒見的你，我的內心在翻騰 <br />\n我的手在顫抖，我的心跳急速的跳起來，我的呼吸.......<br />\n<br />\n我很想問你「你仲有冇嬲我？」<br />\n我很想知道，我緩緩張開了嘴脣，卻發不出聲音，牙齒在微微的顫動，但我卻沒法說出來<br />\n<br />\n我真的很想知道，是真的想知道嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我很怕聽到你的答案，很怕你親口跟我說「我真係好憎你，好嬲你」，甚至在夢中，我也不願聽到你的答案 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我怕了，是因為，現實的我覺得你不會原諒我 <br />\n但我潛意識上也想得到解脫 <br />\n<br />\n每當我想起你，我都會頭皮發麻，呼吸不由自主的加快，我很怕<br />\nYou have been my nightmare for quite a few months <br />\nTo be more precise, I have been my own nightmare since the beginning <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n謝謝，我的潛意識，告訴我其實我的內心很渴望得到解脫<br />\n但我真的很害怕，害怕重啟那段記憶，害怕面對事實，害怕想起當初開心的時光  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n看到現在這樣的我，我自己也想笑<br />\nHow pathetic I am now <br />\nI am the one to blame <br />\nSuch a joke <br />\n也許我真的放唔過自己？我不知道"},{"pid":"8cc9f3eae2b50934a886337db9b2ac5668b26b59","tid":2184040,"uid":341236,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:54:20.000Z","msg":"中文5**"},{"pid":"2a47170fdf2dbdaf7e79965658501ab1f4817b7b","tid":2184040,"uid":304619,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:57:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c379fe05a8ef1937ed8d65646e9d455f70144f2","tid":2184040,"uid":156818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:58:35.000Z","msg":"你開心 我開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a522bcd0ab02ee7120a716162263ea8f858717","tid":2184040,"uid":308450,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T10:02:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c598ce5ba3faf6c2abcc76cd2c315f96ce3cc2ff","tid":2184040,"uid":146299,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T10:03:58.000Z","msg":"秒"},{"pid":"ba9fce861f6e5a0f90d2875d080184aae9fe1b1b","tid":2184040,"uid":341236,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74a522bcd0ab02ee7120a716162263ea8f858717","tid":2184040,"uid":308450,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T10:02:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T10:05:28.000Z","msg":"作者運用多種語言形式<br />\n以向讀者展示出作者本人內心天人交戰、忐忑不安的情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d10efd57e149107e7fa4ded2abcb0a41bdd5fd95","tid":2184040,"uid":341236,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c598ce5ba3faf6c2abcc76cd2c315f96ce3cc2ff","tid":2184040,"uid":146299,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T10:03:58.000Z","msg":"秒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T10:05:50.000Z","msg":"我追蹤左清楚<br />\n你太遲了"},{"pid":"e987fed74ae747f7cf18a25122c12452a113b94a","tid":2184040,"uid":142509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T11:38:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb9661ef44c675be63017df7dea36927bac2ba84","tid":2184040,"uid":248044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T13:11:10.000Z","msg":"都過咗咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唉"},{"pid":"eada981cad3719d0dd3b5fc461bf806b57648ffe","tid":2184040,"uid":181624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T15:31:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}